This case having been finally heard on today the court on the same day delivered
the following :-
ORDER

1. This is a case charge sheeted by the Sub Inspector of Police, Medical College Police
Station in Crime No. 2221/2019 alleging commission of offence u/s 294(b), 506)
t/w 34 of IPC.

2. As per order dated 07/01/2025 in Crl.M.C 4155/2021 of the Honorable High Court of
Kerala, all further proceedings in the case are quashed. Copy of order is produced.
Hence, the case is closed.
